{{Use mdy dates|date=March 2014}} {{Infobox film | name = Anatomy of a Love Seen | image = | alt = | caption = Theatrical release poster | director = Marina Rice Bader | producer = Jan Miller Corran | screenplay = Marina Rice Bader | starring = {{Plainlist| * Sharon Hinnendael * Jill Evyn * Constance Brenneman * Marina Rice Bader }} | music = Thom Robson | cinematography = Justin Kane | editing = Vanara Taing | studio = Soul Kiss Films | distributor = | released = {{Film date|2014|07|18|North America}} | runtime = 80 minutes | country = United States | language = English | budget = | gross = }} '''''Anatomy of a Love Seen''''' is a 2014 American [[romance film|romance]] [[drama]] film written and directed by [[Marina Rice Bader]].<ref>{{Cite web|title = Gravitas Ventures Acquires 'Anatomy of a Love Seen'|url = http://www.indiewire.com/article/gravitas-ventures-acquires-anatomy-of-a-love-seen-20141023|website = Indiewire|accessdate = 2015-12-01}}</ref> The film stars Sharon Hinnendael and Jill Evyn.<ref>{{Cite web|title = Music Video for "Anatomy of a Love Seen" Released|url = http://www.curvemag.com/Reviews/Music-Video-for-Anatomy-of-a-Love-Seen-Released-245/|website = Curve Magazine|accessdate = 2015-12-01}}</ref>
